            <div class="oc-n">31</div>
            <div class="oc-l">Portfolio KPIs formally defined with business &amp; technical owners</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome">
            <div class="oc-n">60%→15%</div>
            <div class="oc-l">Reduction in data team time spent on reconciliation</div>
          </div>
          <div class="outcome">
            <div class="oc-n">1</div>
            <div class="oc-l">Source of truth for loan portfolio — for the first time post-migration</div>
          </div>
        </div>

